</P>
<P>
Election results -- The Long Beach mayoral and Riverside County assessor races 
were incorrectly reported Thursday. Ernie Kell won the Long Beach mayoral race 
with 33,434 votes, followed by Tom Clark with 32,762. In the assessor's race, 
Gary Orso was elected with 86,369 votes, followed by Jim Covell with 62,733. 
</P>
