FEINSTEIN, DIANNE; WILSON, PETE; TELEVISION ADVERTISING; POLITICAL ADVERTISING; 
CALIFORNIA GOVERNOR; VAN DE KAMP, JOHN K; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; FUND 
RAISING; WOMEN -- POLITICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
