COMPEAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Southland Edition, B1) PERSISTENCE: The 
dogged work of a sheriff's deputy in investigating the hit-and-run death of a 
young Mexican immigrant, Jorge Rodelo, above, paid off when Torrance police 
arrested a suspect. 
</P>
