<TEXT>
<P>
The Kings have offered termination contracts to center Mike Allison, wing Chris 
Kontos and backup goalie Mario Gosselin. That makes them free agents until July 
1. Should they fail to sign with another team by then, they can return to the 
Kings for one more season unless the club chooses to buy out their contracts. 
</P>
