Los Angeles Times; Photo, David and Janet Pace have fence around Westminster 
pool although daughter Morgan is not yet walking. KARI RENE HALL / Los Angeles 
Times; Chart, ORANGE COUNTY DROWNING DEATHS, DENNIS LOWE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
